<db:para>The Vulkan Texture Import example shows how an application can import and use a <db:link xlink:href="https://www.khronos.org/registry/vulkan/specs/1.1-extensions/man/html/VkImage.html">VkImage</db:link> in the Qt Quick scene. This provides an alternative to the <db:link xlink:href="qtquick-scenegraph-vulkanunderqml-example.xml">underlay</db:link> or overlay approaches when it comes to integrating native Vulkan rendering.</db:para>
<db:para>This example is equivalent in most ways to the <db:link xlink:href="qtquick-scenegraph-metaltextureimport-example.xml">Metal Texture Import</db:link> example. The Vulkan rendering code is taken from the <db:link xlink:href="qtquick-scenegraph-vulkanunderqml-example.xml">Vulkan Under QML</db:link> example.</db:para>
